       "+------------+----------------------------------------+---------------------+\n",
       "| Variable   | Description                            | Units               |\n",
       "+:===========+:=======================================+:====================+\n",
       "| ADG        | average daily BW gain                  | grams per day (g/d) |\n",
       "+------------+----------------------------------------+---------------------+\n",
